{"tid":2299602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"殘忍！蘋果 M1 版 MacBook 跑《LoL》效能、能耗都贏 Intel 版","createTime":"2020-11-25T02:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T12:19:50.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09ff77a95867dfcbdf1c135d0e1846712c53283a","tid":2299602,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:20:55.000Z","msg":"據 YouTuber「Max Tech」測試，若在 M1 版 MacBook Air 上，以 Rosetta 2 轉譯模擬 X8<br />\n6 版的《英雄聯盟》（League of Legends），不論可執行的畫質、幀率，以及溫度控管方<br />\n面，都明顯勝出 Intel 處理器的版本。<br />\n <br />\n測試結果顯示，作為兩款價錢相同的電腦，M1 版 MacBook Air，除了最高可執行 120fps，<br />\n在預設最高的 2560 * 1600 解析度下，M1 版也能跑出 60 ~ 70 出頭的幀率，相反地搭載<br />\nIntel Core m3 的舊版 MacBook Air，則只有將近砍半的 30 ~ 40fps。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3mfWSyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3mfWSyM&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=eb1af392\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3mfWSyM</a>"},{"pid":"72169014d88336beda852786898f92d6f6914896","tid":2299602,"uid":98473,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"支那lol就算撚數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee79c2804f5eb4e070505611de62f7d82ec24af","tid":2299602,"uid":201489,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"今年年頭部Air個個話正爭住買<br />\n轉個頭就輸晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f46616d3dea9cf0c324f61db99c7c34e433f4a5","tid":2299602,"uid":123020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:27:19.000Z","msg":"文青更係用air番學上網睇yt傾pj<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死毒撚拎黎打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0b0b4260ac6d4af79a0cd4c90eef08f1051ce1","tid":2299602,"uid":126782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72169014d88336beda852786898f92d6f6914896","tid":2299602,"uid":98473,"like":4,"di